e message that every vote matters, he said."},{"pid":"92473fcc501bb61bee3ba4b5f059ffe3f0e80015","tid":1687451,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:19:35.000Z","msg":"個Rachel Leung以前做過cctvb，佢老公又係前cctvb記者，親共好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64887482417cedbc270d1af654ca251960825241","tid":1687451,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a8402a1d4f37a9b2ba1315d613fd7531c3c435","tid":1687451,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053f8cd89f7ba0731f02145db48fd2378f56efaf","tid":1687451,"uid":32148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:40:10.000Z","msg":"民選出嚟既唔批評得？ Amazing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e920527b411802db9157df36ca51df7635f54514","tid":1687451,"uid":237562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:41:47.000Z","msg":"淘寶日報"},{"pid":"17550573973a640a3e95afedf70e02d935ad2585","tid":1687451,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e920527b411802db9157df36ca51df7635f54514","tid":1687451,"uid":237562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:41:47.000Z","msg":"淘寶日報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b64075579785836d27ccb934554ad3ae91203fc","tid":1687451,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa